{"type": "article", "id": 26170, "title": "喵星人爱纸箱？那就把纸箱做成猫屋吧", "description": "猫咪霸占纸箱，主人坐拥世界。", "date": "2016-04-29T07:32:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3033, "name": "猫屋"}, {"id": 920, "name": "家居设计"}, {"id": 26912, "name": "Poopy Cat"}], "category": 17, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 182, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702113603IlrotLyiO25KQCxf.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p align=\"left\">不久前，我们报道了<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/25715.html\">美国公益组织 Architects for Animals 设计的 12 个猫屋</a>。有读者留言说：“猫最后爱上了包装的纸箱。”</p>\n<p align=\"left\">这的确是个好问题。猫咪总是对纸箱一往情深：它是个安全的避风港、捕猎的好场所、温暖的小窝……但主人大概很难容忍一只脏兮兮的纸箱违和地出现在干净房间里。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113554i7gUP3lmIv56BGZf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p align=\"left\">现在，有人想出了个好点子。来自荷兰阿姆斯特丹的 <a href=\"http://www.poopycat.com/en/\">Poppy Cat 创意工作室</a>用纸箱做成了 7 个微缩版世界地标建筑，包括埃及狮身人面像、巴黎埃菲尔铁塔、美国白宫、俄罗斯圣瓦西里大教堂、印度泰姬陵、南亚寺塔和南美玛雅神庙。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">这些纸箱废料搭建的猫屋小巧轻便，涂上颜料后显得精致不少。材质是用两层厚厚的凹槽纸板叠加而成，可承载一位成年男士的重量，所以不用担心它不够坚固。内部设计还增加了一些小细节让猫咪和主人互动。比如埃菲尔铁塔里用绳子挂着个小食盒，主人可以把小零食放在里面，猫咪晃动绳子就可以吃到掉下来的美食。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113555UBNxJShEKWadot1i.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p align=\"left\">至于拼装时间，团队找了几个人试了猫屋系列中最复杂的圣瓦西里大教堂，结果大家 5 分钟就弄好了，围观的喵星人立刻虎扑上来……</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113556OZPVNfpHqmeKD7RQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79584352\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113557EgDRxhyk5FGTwusd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38386308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">俄罗斯圣瓦西里大教堂，内部有小铃铛可以让喵星人拉着玩儿。这个教堂在历史上是为俄罗斯第一位沙皇伊凡雷帝修建的。他没有养猫。不过列宁养了一只，肯定是红色的……</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113557pAC9Z4zPBIU8HJT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113558K9RHsnlurxVNkTdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39119804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">泰姬陵，国王为他的第三位爱妻修建，也适合爱猫。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113558sxVJDB7OUtaeNFYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69315403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021135598hbyQOlTtFgrvP5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38753056\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">狮身人面像。尾部有条小绳子可供猫咪拉着玩儿。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113559qGwfs4JehUcdoVkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79339853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113600ZGgJAUOL2IWCwYaM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38508557\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">南亚寺塔，猫咪可以在里面沉思、发呆、修禅。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113600AFCh6XRTPzHuWnsw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113601htyEzm3gp9cFjWu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39119804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">白宫。从 1800 年起，白宫就是美国总统的住所和办公场所。一共有 11 位美国总统养过猫咪，第一个是林肯。1861 年他养了两只叫 Tobby 和 Dixie 的猫。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113601gH14NSlT3sqXf8Zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021136021pmD6KSviWyuwCZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38875306\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">玛雅神庙，铺在底部的硬纸板专供猫咪挠着玩。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113603GdoQl1HhWC3tIFzv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82518337\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113603pu9KwGNDYSbf0nX7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38630807\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">巴黎铁塔。真实的巴黎铁塔有 324 米高，宠物禁止入内，不过在这个猫屋里就没问题了。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p align=\"left\">这个地标猫屋系列目前还在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/poopycat/cardboard-landmark-play-houses-for-cats-dogs-and-s\">Kickstarter</a> 上募资，已获得 286 人的支持，离目标金额 3 万英镑还差一半。如果喜欢，你可以去支持一下。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTU1MDg3NDQ3Ng==\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; min-height: 240px;\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div>\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">题图、配图、视频来自 </span><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/poopycat/cardboard-landmark-play-houses-for-cats-dogs-and-s\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">kickstarter.com</a><br></p>\n\n\n"}